{"word":"G4371 - προσφάγιον - prosphágion - pros-fag'-ee-on - Meat","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσφάγιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosphágion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-fag'-ee-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Meat</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"மீன் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"anything eaten with bread"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a presumed derivative of a compound of <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G5315 - φάγω - phágō - fag'-o/5315\">G5315</a>; something <i>eaten in addition</i> to bread, that is, a <i>relish</i> (specifically <i>fish</i>; compare <a href=\"#/G3795 - ὀψάριον - opsárion - op-sar'-ee-on/3795\">G3795</a>): - meat.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}